Package: RCX
Type: Package
Title: R package implementing the Cytoscape Exchange (CX) format
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Florian Auer <florian.auer@informatik.uni-augsburg.de>
Maintainer: Florian Auer <florian.auer@informatik.uni-augsburg.de>
Description: Create, handle, validate, visualize and convert networks in the Cytoscape exchange (CX) format to standard data types and objects. The CX format is also used by the NDEx platform, a online commons for biological networks, and the network visualization software Cytocape.
License:  MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    plyr,
    tidyr,
    readr,
    igraph,
    graph
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
biocViews: Pathways, DataImport, Network
Suggests: BiocStyle,
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    base64enc
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
URL: https://github.com/frankkramer-lab/RCX
BugReports: https://github.com/frankkramer-lab/RCX/issues
